data.description: Price Drop. Owner is motivated. Welcome to a renovated, mid-century home located in Southeast Ocala. This spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has been updated with new windows in 2021 and a new water heater in 2022. The electrical was also updated 2021.  The roof was replaced in 2018. Luxury vinyl plank floors, fresh interior paint, newer kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and glass tile backsplash can be found throughout. The oversized family/living room features textured walls commonly seen on HDTV. The bathrooms have been remodeled; the master features a fully tiled walk-in shower with new flooring, newer glass shower door, two vanities, double rain shower heads with sprayers, updated lighting, updated plumbing and a new toilet. The second bathroom features a new tub, subway shower tile, new shower hardware, new vanity, updated lighting, updated plumbing and a new toilet. The washer/dryer hook-ups are located in the utility room just off the epoxied two-car garage. The screened back patio allows for plenty of space to relax after a long day. Loan is assumable if buyer qualifies with lender. LOW interest rate.
